 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"Ching買左幾錢呀～ 請問續航力如何？會唔會好易發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"我i7 個時 79xx<br />\n有個USB 係2.0好奇怪。開個下有好輕微&ldquo;咔&rdquo;一聲。換過部都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n螢幕幾好， NTSC 72% （SWIFT 5 相同）<br />\n<br />\n續航聲稱9-10hrs. 5.5-7hrs左右吧。<br />\n<br />\n i7 風噪聲較高 （買前已知）.<br />\n溫度OK啦，畢竟i7。<br />\n<br />\n一條系統 M.2 NVME SSD， 可再插一條 M2 SATA。問過皇家俱樂部可以自己加。<br />\n4喇叭， 底下2個， 鍵盤左右2個。<br />\n<br />\n其實總體與 SWIFT 5 大部份相同。<br />\n但SWIFT 5 有觸控+PD快充。3年保電1年。<br />\n<br />\nASUS 保2年電1年。靚仔。"},{"pid":"1f1a8e986072af56271b8437cfa0a464a453b9c3","tid":1564744,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4143f4927e16ef79445d6522417017805280655f","tid":1564744,"uid":2390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f439cd3248318248425e8baf8dfb3f715ba0c1","tid":1564744,"uid":305465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"我電腦節買左 UX431FN i7<br />\n<br />\n點解唔買 UX433FN？ <br />\n只有一條M2 SSD槽， WIFI 卡冇得換。<br />\n<br />\n我會再等SWIFT 5 10th i7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T11:05:35.000Z","msg":"Ching買左幾錢呀～ 請問續航力如何？會唔會好易發熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"睇劇3-4粒鐘<br />\n放上大脾會有少少熱但接受到"},{"pid":"2cdfbeeffe664d4d88e19f2de262583e8b67d5b3","tid":1564744,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e6268cb3389cf32655aa097ab8c634fca383bb","tid":1564744,"uid":2390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce404036e1179bb2503751b0c6fb31e383bebc9d","tid":1564744,"uid":69749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdadc99dc3d9a